  "body": "Hi there,\r\n\r\nI'd like to report some missing test cases for instructions which copy memory and the out-of-gas failure is directly result of the additional memory copy cost:\r\n- `KECCAK256`,\r\n- `CODECOPY`,\r\n- `EXTCODECOPY`,\r\n- `RETURNDATACOPY`.\r\n\r\n---\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/573380/116072321-35518080-a68f-11eb-853f-da0cce9a6393.png)\r\n---\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/573380/116072387-4ac6aa80-a68f-11eb-881c-31a1cf82f259.png)\r\n---\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/573380/116072778-d5a7a500-a68f-11eb-867e-86f35d9a876c.png)\r\n\r\nThe coverage is from https://github.com/ethereum/evmone. \r\nhttps://codecov.io/gh/ethereum/evmone/src/eeea491ed8d8cb29c895131a97feabc8a125c542/lib/evmone/instructions.hpp.",
